---
// 문의 티켓 페이지 셸. 기존 public/tickets.html 과 동일한 마커/구조를 유지하되,
// header/sidebar/footer 를 빌드 타임에 컴포넌트로 인라인한다(런타임 placeholder 주입 불필요).
// base CDN 은 BaseLayout 이 빌드 타임에 인라인(베이킹) — PAGE_BUNDLES['/tickets.html']=['base','markdown','editor']기준으로 베이킹.
// render.css/mini-editor.css/image-editor.css/image-picker.css 는 본문 렌더링·미니 에디터·이미지 편집용으로 head 슬롯에서 직접 로드.
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout pagePath="/tickets.html" title="티켓 문의 - CloudWiki">
    <Fragment slot="head">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/render.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mini-editor.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/image-editor.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/image-picker.css" />
        <!-- 테마 FOUC 방지: CSS 로드 후 즉시 테마 적용 -->
        <script is:inline>try{var t=localStorage.getItem('themeMode');if(t==='light'||t==='dark')document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme',t);}catch(e){}</script>
        <style is:inline>
            /* 모바일에서 햄버거 메뉴 숨김 */
            .navbar-toggler[data-bs-target="#mobileSidebar"] {
                display: none !important;
            }
            /* 댓글 본문 (.wiki-content) 의 마진/여백을 티켓 댓글 카드용으로 조이기 */
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content > :first-child { margin-top: 0; }
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content > :last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content p { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content h1,
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content h2,
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content h3,
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content h4,
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content h5,
            .discussion-comment-body.wiki-content h6 {
                font-size: 1.05rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            }
        </style>
    </Fragment>

    <!-- ── 네비게이션 바 ── -->
    <Header />

    <!-- ── 메인 레이아웃 ── -->
    <div class="wiki-layout">
        <div class="wiki-container">
            <!-- 로딩 -->
            <div id="loading" class="wiki-loading">
                <div class="spinner-border text-primary" role="status"></div>
                <span>불러오는 중...</span>
            </div>

            <!-- 티켓 목록 페이지 -->
            <div id="ticketListPage" class="d-none">
                <div class="wiki-article">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                        <h2><i class="bi bi-ticket-detailed"></i> 티켓 문의</h2>
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-wiki btn-sm d-none" id="newTicketBtn" onclick="showNewTicketForm()">
                                <i class="bi bi-plus-lg"></i> 새 문의
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 필터 영역 -->
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3 align-items-center">
                        <!-- 상태 필터 -->
                        <div class="btn-group btn-group-sm" role="group">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary active"
                                onclick="filterTickets(this, 'status', '')">
                                전체
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-success" onclick="filterTickets(this, 'status', 'open')">
                                <i class="bi bi-circle-fill text-success" style="font-size:0.5em"></i> 열림
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-danger" onclick="filterTickets(this, 'status', 'closed')">
                                <i class="bi bi-circle-fill text-danger" style="font-size:0.5em"></i> 닫힘
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 유형 필터 (관리자용) -->
                        <select class="form-select form-select-sm d-none" id="typeFilter" style="width: auto; min-width: 120px;"
                            onchange="applyTypeFilter()">
                            <option value="">유형: 전체</option>
                            <option value="general">일반</option>
                            <option value="document">문서</option>
                            <option value="discussion">토론</option>
                            <option value="account">계정</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 새 티켓 폼 -->
                    <div id="newTicketForm" class="d-none mb-4">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">새 문의 작성</h5>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label">문의 유형</label>
                                    <select class="form-select" id="newTicketType">
                                        <option value="general">일반</option>
                                        <option value="document">문서</option>
                                        <option value="discussion">토론</option>
                                        <option value="account">계정</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="newTicketTitle" placeholder="문의 제목">
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <div id="newTicketContent"></div>
                                    <!-- 미니 에디터(CM6) 로드 실패 시 fallback. 미니 에디터 마운트 성공 시 숨겨진다. -->
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="newTicketContentFallback" rows="4"
                                        placeholder="문의 내용을 입력하세요"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                                    <button class="btn btn-wiki btn-sm" onclick="submitNewTicket()">작성</button>
                                    <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm"
                                        onclick="document.getElementById('newTicketForm').classList.add('d-none')">취소</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="ticketsList"></div>

                    <!-- 페이지네이션 -->
                    <div id="ticketPagination" class="d-none text-center py-3">
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" id="loadMoreBtn" onclick="loadMoreTickets()">
                            <i class="mdi mdi-arrow-down"></i> 더 불러오기
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 티켓 상세 페이지 -->
            <div id="ticketDetailPage" class="d-none">
                <div class="wiki-article">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                        <h2 id="ticketTitle"></h2>
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <a href="/tickets" class="btn btn-wiki-outline btn-sm">
                                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> 목록
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-3" id="ticketMeta"></div>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-2 mb-4" id="ticketActions"></div>

                    <div id="commentsList"></div>

                    <!-- 댓글 작성 폼 -->
                    <div id="commentForm" class="mt-4">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h6 class="card-title">댓글 작성</h6>
                                <div id="replyQuote" class="d-none mb-2"></div>
                                <input type="hidden" id="replyParentId" value="">
                                <div class="mb-2">
                                    <div id="commentContent"></div>
                                    <!-- 미니 에디터 로드 실패 시 fallback -->
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="commentContentFallback" rows="3"
                                        placeholder="댓글을 입력하세요"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                                    <button class="btn btn-wiki btn-sm" onclick="submitComment()">작성</button>
                                    <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm d-none" id="cancelReplyBtn" onclick="cancelReply()">답글
                                        취소</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 오른쪽 사이드바 (PC 전용 오프캔버스 컨테이너) -->
        <aside class="wiki-sidebar d-none" id="wikiSidebar">
            <Sidebar />
        </aside>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 푸터 ── -->
    <Footer />

    <!-- ── 이미지 편집 모달 (handleImageUpload 가 사용) ── -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="imageEditorModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" data-bs-backdrop="static">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h6 class="modal-title"><i class="bi bi-crop"></i> 이미지 편집</h6>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="닫기"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="img-editor-canvas-wrap" id="imgEditorCanvasWrap">
                        <canvas id="imgEditorCanvas"></canvas>
                        <div class="crop-overlay" id="cropOverlay" style="display:none;">
                            <div class="crop-box" id="cropBox">
                                <div class="crop-handle tl" data-handle="tl"></div>
                                <div class="crop-handle tr" data-handle="tr"></div>
                                <div class="crop-handle bl" data-handle="bl"></div>
                                <div class="crop-handle br" data-handle="br"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="img-editor-toolbar">
                        <button type="button" id="btnCropToggle" title="크롭 모드 전환"><i class="bi bi-crop"></i></button>
                        <button type="button" id="btnCropApply" style="display:none;" title="크롭 적용"><i class="bi bi-check-lg"></i></button>
                        <div class="separator"></div>
                        <button type="button" id="btnRotateLeft" title="왼쪽 90도 회전"><i class="bi bi-arrow-counterclockwise"></i></button>
                        <button type="button" id="btnRotateRight" title="오른쪽 90도 회전"><i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i></button>
                        <div class="separator"></div>
                        <button type="button" id="btnImgReset" title="원본 복원"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> 초기화</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="img-editor-info" id="imgEditorInfo"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center w-100">
                    <div class="dropdown">
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm dropdown-toggle" type="button"
                            id="btnImgEditorSizeToggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                            <i class="mdi mdi-arrow-expand-all me-1"></i>크게(기본)
                        </button>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu" id="imgEditorSizeDropdown" aria-labelledby="btnImgEditorSizeToggle">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" data-size="icon"><i class="mdi mdi-square-medium-outline me-2"></i>아이콘</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" data-size="small"><i class="mdi mdi-arrow-collapse me-2"></i>작게</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" data-size="medium"><i class="mdi mdi-square-outline me-2"></i>중간</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" data-size="full"><i class="mdi mdi-arrow-expand-all me-2"></i>크게(기본)</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">취소</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" id="btnImgEditorDone"><i class="bi bi-check-lg"></i> 편집 완료</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <Fragment slot="scripts">
        <script type="module" src="/dist/common.js" is:inline></script>
        <script type="module" src="/dist/render.js" is:inline></script>
        <script type="module" src="/dist/edit-image.js" is:inline></script>
        <script type="module" src="/dist/discussion-edit.js" is:inline></script>
        <script type="module" src="/dist/tickets.js" is:inline></script>
    </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
